{"tid":966273,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己患抑鬱症","createTime":"2019-01-02T16:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T07:30:54.000Z","uid":226913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9e09d7b5e046be1cd60b1ee7f311ce3124c70b16","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:14:49.000Z","msg":"本身份工好似唔錯，經常要出差（每月1-2星期），人工算過得去咁啦<br />\n<br />\n但最近一年，覺得自己精神狀態愈來愈差，而且對好多嘢失去興趣（以前會打波，打拳，玩樂器等），漸漸唔鐘意social，節日完全唔想出街<br />\n<br />\n慢慢開始影響工作表現，從而引起惡性循環，表現愈差壓力愈大，壓力愈大愈覺得灰心，間中甚至有傷害自己的念頭<br />\n<br />\n我本身自尊心好強，唔鐘意人可憐我，但當發現問題變得嚴重，有開始嘗試同朋友傾訴<br />\n<br />\n上網做咗個depression test，結果係moderate to severe depression，不過唔知準唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔想睇醫生，因為我知食藥都係治標不治本<br />\n<br />\n而家開始揾工，希望轉下環境會好些<br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇人同我情況相似？"},{"pid":"9a4cf29c39f769df9d631023729bc7e1d52a618d","tid":966273,"uid":125561,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"食藥治標唔治本呢個概念未必啱喎 好多人抑鬱係內分泌問題"},{"pid":"16b3d446da5a05d98dd6ae1a012ccbfe3fb09ae8","tid":966273,"uid":158837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:43:32.000Z","msg":"同你情況有啲似 <br />\n好迷失 唔想面對人群"},{"pid":"4c1d5a881725edac3c08bcf4f2b6ef505f5b51ce","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a4cf29c39f769df9d631023729bc7e1d52a618d","tid":966273,"uid":125561,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"食藥治標唔治本呢個概念未必啱喎 好多人抑鬱係內分泌問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:45:15.000Z","msg":"唔知係內分泌影響情緒，定情緒影響內分泌<br />\n<br />\n但我知食藥會變得依賴，到時想停藥都停唔到"},{"pid":"4993687b89171e6a050b14de5a135a62a372719d","tid":966273,"uid":185092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:51:59.000Z","msg":"見心理學家"},{"pid":"c44bd20999fe2eb2718f46f5e130a21a5609f421","tid":966273,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n唔知邊度有醫生睇<br />\n同點搵"},{"pid":"28bfc21bc3d02d3c44cff6cb02d475d60f42bfd7","tid":966273,"uid":225733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:58:11.000Z","msg":"漸漸"},{"pid":"9b8a3a3e2bdf6459e36704e072d0b0a8e4f3587e","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係咪自己嘅性格唔適合呢個社會<br />\n<br />\n但係我以前都算係樂觀積極嗰批<br />\n<br />\n可能係呢幾年各方面嘅壓力累積而成，自己以為manage到，但到呢一刻我發現其實問題已經幾嚴重"},{"pid":"e17ca99f9d94498e12062dacc0a75d084a485f87","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c44bd20999fe2eb2718f46f5e130a21a5609f421","tid":966273,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n唔知邊度有醫生睇<br />\n同點搵"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:07:28.000Z","msg":"政府精神科排N年<br />\n<br />\n私家又貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc8f041b294be37a21f44fede99f67dee492f209","tid":966273,"uid":81657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔好返工喇，想做就去做下義工，放鬆啲啦"},{"pid":"2e57921f5e1111237dbb355f6439b0921cec02bf","tid":966273,"uid":194015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c44bd20999fe2eb2718f46f5e130a21a5609f421","tid":966273,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"同問<br />\n唔知邊度有醫生睇<br />\n同點搵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:10:29.000Z","msg":"你上網打精神科醫生就會有好多， 大部分都係喺旺角、尖沙咀、中環"},{"pid":"a0ab15786e530e0b489959f13bc1fa44a0d6bc3c","tid":966273,"uid":182195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:13:46.000Z","msg":"搵社工先，再轉介去精神科"},{"pid":"0d83dc099662db5e8cf9e1b5af68fcf3a0ffac00","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc8f041b294be37a21f44fede99f67dee492f209","tid":966273,"uid":81657,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"唔好返工喇，想做就去做下義工，放鬆啲啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:14:17.000Z","msg":"唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一邊供樓一邊交緊租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 過埋呢幾個月可能輕鬆d<br />\n<br />\n其實我都有諗過做有份意義d嘅工，有冇好介紹"},{"pid":"2466247fdc00370f8af52726d24b47ee1265331e","tid":966273,"uid":162377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生。<br />\n專業人士當面評估比網上評估準確<br />\n有冇都冇所謂，只係一個病嚟，唔使睇得好嚴重，但又唔好太忽視，因為畢竟日常生活被影響到"},{"pid":"4bcee11edc0cb2f7be014ca21db29e1d4f86b5af","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2466247fdc00370f8af52726d24b47ee1265331e","tid":966273,"uid":162377,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:14:21.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生。<br />\n專業人士當面評估比網上評估準確<br />\n有冇都冇所謂，只係一個病嚟，唔使睇得好嚴重，但又唔好太忽視，因為畢竟日常生活被影響到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:40:08.000Z","msg":"都要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0bedf9fa5d14e3ed367692e506c24bdf12f934","tid":966273,"uid":173814,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:17:29.000Z","msg":"有病就要食藥架啦，長期病咪要長期食藥<br />\n全身所有病都係咁醫架啦，咁樣執番條命仔都叫依賴？<br />\n<br />\nDepression 係會致命的，早日求醫啦"},{"pid":"29f5bfb978ef56fee8a8799db6eb4bc355f1b766","tid":966273,"uid":72034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:19:44.000Z","msg":"其實如果去睇，要去邊到睇？同埋要幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a50c369ee9e69f7f9d6c3fa8f78d39be7bb5f1","tid":966273,"uid":18552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9b8a3a3e2bdf6459e36704e072d0b0a8e4f3587e","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係咪自己嘅性格唔適合呢個社會<br />\n<br />\n但係我以前都算係樂觀積極嗰批<br />\n<br />\n可能係呢幾年各方面嘅壓力累積而成，自己以為manage到，但到呢一刻我發現其實問題已經幾嚴重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"屌我都係咁，<br />\n我以前係正面撚，<br />\n依家所有野都係諗閪野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家每日訓醒 就係諗點解仲未死。"},{"pid":"1fafb059f26f1617b4dccb4fb5ea8c42fdbcd35d","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:49:52.000Z","msg":"啱啱打電話去醫管局24小時精神科熱線（2466 7350）<br />\n<br />\n佢叫我去綜合心理健康約個時間，佢話快過普通門診"},{"pid":"46e9369ddbcb0b0ed20b60c3672c8386e0cc2683","tid":966273,"uid":25512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:53:53.000Z","msg":"試下搵輔導中心去傾下<br />\n不過內心既野<br />\n要明白唔能夠一時三刻搞得掂<br />\n<br />\n撐住"},{"pid":"e1ed3e35630af1acacf3c5a755a030d8f4cf4948","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a50c369ee9e69f7f9d6c3fa8f78d39be7bb5f1","tid":966273,"uid":18552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9b8a3a3e2bdf6459e36704e072d0b0a8e4f3587e","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:06:13.000Z","msg":"我有諗過係咪自己嘅性格唔適合呢個社會<br />\n<br />\n但係我以前都算係樂觀積極嗰批<br />\n<br />\n可能係呢幾年各方面嘅壓力累積而成，自己以為manage到，但到呢一刻我發現其實問題已經幾嚴重"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:42:41.000Z","msg":"屌我都係咁，<br />\n我以前係正面撚，<br />\n依家所有野都係諗閪野先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家每日訓醒 就係諗點解仲未死。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:54:54.000Z","msg":"我有時會想像自己意外死鳩咗<br />\n<br />\n咁樣死得有尊嚴d"},{"pid":"549bf106203e4984f4bbdc543955ad2739258f14","tid":966273,"uid":22069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:56:10.000Z","msg":"試過 出去打下波約下fd睇要病無好轉先啦"},{"pid":"68b1af52edc4f97b9fdcb67102944f6481a70b57","tid":966273,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ed3e35630af1acacf3c5a755a030d8f4cf4948","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68a50c369ee9e69f7f9d6c3fa8f78d39be7bb5f1","tid":966273,"uid":18552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9b8a3a3e2bdf6459e36704e072d0b0a8e4f3587e","tid":966273,"uid":226913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"re